title: The Haves and The Have Nots S01E20.mp4
description:
Tyler Perry's The Haves and the Have Nots


Season 1 [Part 2] (2014)


Episode 20: "Unanswered Calls":


Jeffery begins to realize that Wyatt may be responsible for killing Lizzie, the 

little girl whose death has dominated the local news coverage, as well as for 

critically injuring Candace's brother, Benny. Wyatt begs Jeffery not to expose his 

secret, and Jeffery promises not to.


At the courthouse, Candace tries to secure Amanda's inheritance, but her threats 

against Jim fall on deaf ears. Will she go to the press with her story?


Later, Maggie tells Jim to wait to announce his candidacy for governor, and urges 

him and David to attend Lizzie's funeral to help subdue public outrage over the 

girl's death. Jim agrees to go while keeping his secret that Lizzie was killed by 

his own son, Wyatt.
